author: jwross
msg: Add debug logging for unrecognized resources in the subsystem archive.
Subsystems will now output a debug logging message when an unrecognized resource is encountered in the subsystem archive. The
level is debug because of the possibility of false positives if the provider knowingly stored resources in the archive that
are neither bundles nor subsystems. The following is an example of what the output might look like.
"file:/C:/Users/IBM_AD~1/AppData/Local/Temp/paxexam_runner_jwrossjr/application.a.esa" will be ignored because it is not
